    <briefdescription>
<para>Immutable record representing a single scheduled event in the simulation timeline. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implements <computeroutput>IComparable&lt;SimEvent&gt;</computeroutput> so that instances can be stored directly in a <computeroutput>SortedSet</computeroutput> inside <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_core_1_1_event_queue" kindref="compound">EventQueue</ref>. Ordering is by <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_core_1_1_sim_event_1a607c1c72df770a64614efd6de3cd4698" kindref="member">Time</ref> ascending, with <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_core_1_1_sim_event_1ab56cee8678fd0b8f95a8aa4b18bf4fc8" kindref="member">SequenceNumber</ref> as a FIFO tiebreaker for events scheduled at the same instant. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
